solution.p:
So, the volume of a tetrahedron with side length \ell is:


\mbox{Volume}&=\int_0^{\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}\ell}\frac{3\sqrt{3}}{8}y^2\dee{y}

&=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{8}\cdot \left(\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}\ell\right)^3=\frac{\sqrt{2}}{12}\ell^3

